title: Fangzhou Yu
text:
I am a PhD student in UNSW, Business School under supervision of Scientia Professor Robert Kohn and Associate Professor Seojeong Lee.
My main research interests include estimation and inference of heterogeneous treatment effect and the application of influence function in sensitivity analysis.
